    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just really scary because it's so much worse than my usual ones. but since it feels similar to the aura i get during migraines, do u think i should just take some extra ibuprofen and try to sleep it off? i really dont want to go to the er if i can help it, it's such a hassle.",
