      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i've had crazy migraines before and they did feel like this. it's probably just a complication or something from stress. if i take a really high dose of ibuprofen or maybe some more stronger stuff i have in my cabinet, could that just knock out the pain so i can sleep? i feel like if i can just get the pain to stop, the face thing will go away too.",
